is incredibly sacred,

00:07:19.820 --> 00:07:21.470 align:middle line:90%
yet incredibly dangerous.

00:07:21.470 --> 00:07:23.940 align:middle line:90%
[RUSHING WATER]

00:07:23.940 --> 00:07:30.235 align:middle line:90%


00:07:30.235 --> 00:07:31.360 align:middle line:10%
>> And then they come here.

