00:07:32.530 --> 00:07:37.270 align:middle line:10%
They forget that she is
also a fierce mother, eh?

00:07:37.270 --> 00:07:38.575 align:middle line:10%
So they think, oh.

00:07:38.575 --> 00:07:39.910 align:middle line:10%
So they get so excited.

00:07:39.910 --> 00:07:43.380 align:middle line:10%
They think it's a part-- becomes
part of a religious thing,

00:07:43.380 --> 00:07:44.180 align:middle line:10%
right?

