So they go and they
dip and they get

00:07:45.400 --> 00:07:47.400 align:middle line:10%
so excited that they are
in the Ganga, you know,

00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:51.270 align:middle line:10%
which is the
epitome of Hinduism.

